      "id": "PopularPost344306",
      "post_content": "How to make this weaker than Condescend without being strictly worse? It is indeed a conundrum. I would've gone with a [Spell Pierce](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Pierce) variant, or better yet, the opposite:  \n  \n![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol)  \nCounter target creature spell unless its controller pays ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol). Scry 1.",
